<P>A relatively small flightless avian race with very few feathers and =
pink=20
skin.</P>
<P>They are a somewhat aggressive species but are also especially =
cautious and=20
quick to scare in to retaliation.</P>
<P>Long ago, the Avian Yl'ta were a race that was consumed by it's =
greed. They=20
laboured, betrayed and fought wars over material wealth idolising wealth =
itself=20
as the single path to ascension. When their empire collapsed and it's =
leaders=20
fell to it's enemies, their planet fell under a dark shadow and anarchy=20
reigned.</P>
<P>This was until a time that is told of where the sky was rent in two =
and the=20
race was gifted with tools of creation and untold power. This gift led =
them to=20
the stars and forever since the Empire has held skills and knowledge =
above=20
simple wealth.</P>
<P>The Yl'ta seek to know the Galaxy, it's wonders and what rarities it =
hides.=20
Despite the empire's goals and recent change in ethos it's people's =
happyness=20
and productivity is largely affected by rarities and wealth the planets =
has=20
found access to.</P>
<P>The Yl'ta typically live in familial dwellings in high altitude areas =
of=20
continental planets.</P>
<P>The Yl'ta prefer Beam Weapons and Fighters with an Efficiency Energy =
Research=20
focus.</P></FONT></DIV></BODY></HTML>

